The README file is a text file that explains what a project is.
It should contain information on

1. GNU General Public License
2. Sasa Kuzmanovic
3. Clone the project, open the terminal inside the Lab you want to start and type in make in the terminal
4. Mutex, condition_variable, chrono, iostream, vector, thread
5. -
6. 	Barrier.h - Declares Barrier objects, and declares the wait function alongside the destructor
	Barrier.cpp - Defines the wait function and the destructor
	Semaphore.h - Declares Signal and Wait functions and holds variables
	Semaphore.cpp - Defines the Wait and Signal functions
	main.cpp - Combines Barriers and Semaphores, makes it run
7. Any other relevent information
